{"tid":2129291,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無拓哥係藍/紅嘅實質證據","createTime":"2020-07-28T13:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T14:13:36.000Z","uid":27120,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a064802b07df573c098309d0221045118ae5b9","tid":2129291,"uid":27120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"家父係淺黃<br />\n平時會睇老蕭/劉細良/852嗰啲<br />\n但有個問題係佢好鐘意睇拓哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話佢英文又好又高大又有鬼妹女朋友<br />\n同佢講咗好多次拓哥係藍佢又問返我有無啲實質證據<br />\n我Google咗但淨係搵到兩登話佢係藍嘅comment<br />\n最多都係話佢掛住吃喝玩樂無為香港發過聲<br />\n但咁樣好難令家父信服（佢會覺得唔發聲唔代表係藍）<br />\n佢知拓哥幾年前喺支那做過街訪<br />\n但又會話係佢初出道嘅事宜家已經無做<br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲打可以俾多啲料救我老豆脫離苦海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a387c23e4285f34e435a17f9001869845a72b3d","tid":2129291,"uid":216555,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8be093f0d721a39832dd6f51229ee52658e9d057","tid":2129291,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T13:19:01.000Z","msg":"dim sum daily佢有份<br />\n英文fake news專抹黑香港"},{"pid":"f9353c8724287dcab9c356e858072fff9008b1cb","tid":2129291,"uid":37874,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdijkc8.png&amp;h=ef7a4bae&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"19a8031bc029e64b833c52513a18d692c4c366a5","tid":2129291,"uid":27120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8be093f0d721a39832dd6f51229ee52658e9d057","tid":2129291,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T13:19:01.000Z","msg":"dim sum daily佢有份<br />\n英文fake news專抹黑香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/selina_cheng/status/1173535915119013888?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fselina_cheng%2Fstatus%2F1173535915119